{"tid":673111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"HKU SPACE電競文憑 7 月開課","createTime":"2018-05-21T14:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T13:07:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":27,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"bc810a421b0f07f2529fd568596aeeed7f31b8a3","tid":673111,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:24:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2075000/2077672/cover_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2075000%2F2077672%2Fcover_1024.jpg&h=e1ac73d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【e-zone 專訊】電子競技（eSports）在 2017 年行業規模已達 6.6 億美元，預計在 2018 年增至 9 億美元，數碼港行政總裁任景信（上圖左）指出注重新舊經濟融合，亦相信推動電競可同時令整個資訊科技產業成長，受益人士比想像中多，未來政府會有港幣 1 億元撥款，把數碼港商場改建為電競場地，讓業界人士毋須再擔心場地問題。<br />\n<br />\n數碼港宣布與港大專業進修學院（HKU SPACE）合作，推動「電子競技科學文憑」課程。該學院院長李經文（圖右）強調電競並非遊戲而已，是一項有組織與紀律的活動，而且產業成長空間大。想知課程內容有乜學？就要留意以下列表：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2075000/2077672/HKU1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2075000%2F2077672%2FHKU1_600.jpg&h=717cdea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n此項課程將於今年 6 月起接受報名，7 月開始授課。另外，火狗創意董事總經理彭子傑指出，本地一切運作成本昂貴，過往亦難以吸引新人入行。然而他強調，香港有能力 IT 系統與遊戲開發等的上遊產業開發取得優勢，未來有能力取得爆炸性成長。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2077672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2077672&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=3ce586e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2077672</a>"},{"pid":"caad184c31c1cd8a61b31d7e93434e6a9fb265ea","tid":673111,"uid":23878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:25:20.000Z","msg":"xxx傳意技巧"},{"pid":"f72df65d2e95814b06e34cb2e1f531edcaf40916","tid":673111,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:26:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hkuspace.hku.hk/cht/prog/dip-in-esports-science\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkuspace.hku.hk%2Fcht%2Fprog%2Fdip-in-esports-science&d=QCkAzDZkjj3i0qnYFRiarcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=51aa7592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkuspace.hku.hk/cht/prog/dip-in-esports-science</a>"},{"pid":"00a2ec9177c7294d7a7cd4d2a4c4a0861aef74fd","tid":673111,"uid":174115,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:29:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/21/222903_42462aa5184c35a0473825df8e282272.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F21%2F222903_42462aa5184c35a0473825df8e282272.png&h=8f201547&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫個導師過黎隻抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"fea0bba09deacd3236e3e5cea28d23d2bd320aa8","tid":673111,"uid":36178,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:34:26.000Z","msg":"全中文就蒜鳩掃把啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"537c38398acc32f5685178853b3d2d8c47c907f6","tid":673111,"uid":82929,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:36:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪痴撚左線<br />\n踢足球都唔會有文憑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af85f713829ac70a895127e5635d64d770fad635","tid":673111,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-21T14:39:38.000Z","msg":"點解唔駛學點砌電競椅，唔駛學點改良